# FXAA Test Mesh by DirectX11 Persona
# This mesh is designed to create significant geometric aliasing.

# Vertices
# Central Cube
v -0.5 -0.5 -0.5
v  0.5 -0.5 -0.5
v  0.5  0.5 -0.5
v -0.5  0.5 -0.5
v -0.5 -0.5  0.5
